      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "We are honored to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, a specimen that defines the standard for 'mint' condition. This automobile has been maintained to an exacting degree, presenting an unblemished exterior and an interior that remains in showroom state. Every mechanical system has been thoroughly vetted to ensure performance that mirrors its original factory specifications. For the collector or enthusiast who prioritizes absolute integrity and aesthetic perfection, this vehicle represents a rare and definitive acquisition opportunity.",
