      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to find a new home for this absolute beauty! Honestly, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today\u2014it is in truly incredible shape. The paint is flawless, the interior is spotless, and it drives like a total dream. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate a car that feels practically brand new. Come take a look and see for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
