      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman in Graphite Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a factory-fresh finish with a professional ceramic coating, showing zero rock chips or swirl marks. Inside, the Agate Grey leather remains supple and taut, with no creasing or signs of use. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This car has been serviced exclusively at authorized Porsche dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. With exceptionally low mileage and a flawless mechanical bill of health, this is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a modern masterpiece in its purest form.",
