    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting professional standards. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a legacy of meticulous care. Mechanically beyond reproach and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality and peak performance.",
