      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood, the S54 3.2L inline-six features six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This chassis has undergone a comprehensive mechanical refresh, including proactive rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. Every bushing and suspension component remains within factory tolerances, providing the precise turn-in and communicative steering feedback that defined this generation. Truly a turn-key, investment-grade driver's car.",
